nt-family: 微软雅黑,Microsoft YaHei; font-size: 14px;\"><span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑,Microsoft YaHei; font-size: 14px;\"><span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑,Microsoft YaHei; font-size: 14px;\">根据对比其他微信商城系统，我们推出基础版小程序本身开源免费，但营销插件、安装服务、服务器和页面设计是收费的项目。我们现在做了一个非常优惠的套餐，3000元包一个无线流量，1m带宽的服务器（880），赠送安装对接服务、二级域名一个、https证书和页面调整服务（定制版根据商家要求另计）。次年如果不用其他服务的，每年只需要支付服务器及证书的费用，大概是1000块左右。<br/></span></span></span></p><p style=\"line-height: 1.75em; text-indent: 2em;\"><strong><span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑,Microsoft YaHei; font-size: 14px;\"><span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑,Microsoft YaHei; font-size: 14px;\"><span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑,Microsoft YaHei; font-size: 14px;\">四、我们的案例<span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑,Microsoft YaHei; font-size: 14px;\"><span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑,Microsoft YaHei; font-size: 14px;\"><span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑,Microsoft YaHei; font-size: 14px;\"><br/></span></span></span></span></span></span></strong></p><p style=\"text-align: center;\"><img width=\"344\" height=\"343\" title=\"同兴源\" style=\"width: 120px; height: 111px; float: none;\" src=\"/Uploads/Editor/2018-09-07/5b923d7c02bea.jpg\"/>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;<strong>.同兴源</strong>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;<img width=\"430\" height=\"430\" title=\"千年古陶\" style=\"width: 109px; height: 111px;\" src=\"/Uploads/Editor/2018-09-07/5b923d7c1df0b.jpg\"/><strong>.<strong>千年古陶</strong></strong></p><p style=\"text-align: center;\"><br/></p><p style=\"line-height: 1.75em; text-indent: 2em;\"><span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑,Microsoft YaHei; font-size: 14px;\"><span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑,Microsoft YaHei; font-size: 14px;\"><span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑,Microsoft YaHei; font-size: 14px;\"><br/></span></span></span><br/></p>',0),(293,'<p><br/></p><p style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑;\"><img title=\"banner01.jpg\" src=\"/Uploads/Editor/2018-09-07/5b924bd6af4b6.jpg\"/></span></p><p style=\"line-height: 2em; text-indent: 2em;\"><span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑,Microsoft YaHei; font-size: 14px;\">根据腾讯最新公布的数据，截止2018年6月底，微信和WeChat合并月活跃帐户已达10.58亿，一个季度增加1300万，同比增长9.9％，持续保持高速发展。同时，微信支付业务的月活跃账户也已超过8亿，日均成交量同比上升超过40％。<br/></span></p><p style=\"line-height: 2em; text-indent: 2em;\"><span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑,Microsoft YaHei; font-size: 14px;\">微信同时披露，得益于智慧零售、高频小额支付场景解决方案，微信支付业务的线下商业支付笔数保持快速增长，同比增幅达280％，而且商业支付笔数占总交易笔数的比例首次超过50％。<br/></span></p><p style=\"line-height: 2em; text-indent: 2em;\"><span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑,Microsoft YaHei; font-size: 14px;\">从趋势发展看，微信商城未来潜力巨大，流量将不断扩大，入驻商家将越来越多，商城系统将更加成熟完善，更加贴近人们生活，甚至改变人们消费生活习惯。<br/></span></p><p style=\"line-height: 2em; text-indent: 2em;\"><span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑,Microsoft YaHei; font-size: 14px;\">假如商家搭建了自己的微信商城，那又该如何让商城一骑绝尘呢？小编窃以为，有如下三点：<br/></span></p><p style=\"line-height: 2em; text-indent: 2em;\"><strong><span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑,Microsoft YaHei; font-size: 14px;\">1.丰富商城的营销插件</span></strong><span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑,Microsoft YaHei; font-size: 14px;\"><br/></span></p><p style=\"line-height: 2em; text-indent: 2em;\"><span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑,Microsoft YaHei; font-size: 14px;\">所谓无利不往，营销插件可以帮助商城带来良好的营销效果，同时也能吸引更多消费者来到商城参观，间接或直接开发意向客户。<br/></span></p><p style=\"line-height: 2em; text-indent: 2em;\"><strong><span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑,Microsoft YaHei; font-size: 14px;\">2.美化自己的微信商城<br/></span></strong></p><p style=\"line-height: 2em; text-indent: 2em;\"><span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑,Microsoft YaHei; font-size: 14px;\">个性化自己的商城，以吸引消费者驻足，将自己的商城装修出自己的特色，让商城更具美感，同时让它更加满足用户体验。<br/></span></p><p style=\"line-height: 2em; text-indent: 2em;\"><strong><span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑,Microsoft YaHei; font-size: 14px;\">3.琳琅满目的商品填充</span></strong><span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑,Microsoft YaHei; font-size: 14px;\"><br/></span></p><p style=\"line-height: 2em; text-indent: 2em;\"><span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑,Microsoft YaHei; font-size: 14px;\">微信客户一般通过搜索进入商城，微信流量入口大，客户来源地也各不相同，商品需要也不尽相同，商品选择也各不相同，所以商城齐全的商品品种配套是必备条件，如果没有琳琅满目的商品，那谈何让顾客选择，谈何促成二次消费？<br/></span></p><p style=\"line-height: 2em; text-indent: 2em;\"><span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑,Microsoft YaHei; font-size: 14px;\">做到以上三点可以让你的微信商城焕然一新，焕发勃勃生机，也可以让你在微信潮流中畅享红利。<br/></span></p><p style=\"line-height: 2em; text-indent: 2em;\"><span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑,Microsoft YaHei; font-size: 14px;\">几何线<a title=\"\" href=\"https://www.jihexian.com/article/detail/id/292.html\" target=\"_self\">微信商城系统</a>团队可以帮助您搭建商城，也可以为你开发丰富的营销插件。<br/></span></p>',0),(294,'<p style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(51, 51, 51); text-transform: none; text-indent: 28px; letter-spacing: normal; font-family: 微软雅黑, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;; font-size: 14px; font-style: normal; font-weight: 400; word-spacing: 0px; float: none; display: inline !important; white-space: normal; orphans: 2; widows: 2; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; text-decoration-style: initial; text-decoration-color: initial;\">&nbsp;<img title=\"2.png\" src=\"/Uploads/Editor/2018-09-10/5b95d28c203d8.png\"/></span></p><p style=\"line-height: 2em;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(51, 51, 51); text-transform: none; text-indent: 28px; letter-spacing: normal; font-family: 微软雅黑, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;; font-size: 14px; font-style: normal; font-weight: 400; word-spacing: 0px; float: none; display: inline !important; white-space: normal; orphans: 2; widows: 2; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; text-decoration-style: initial; text-decoration-color: initial;\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;</span></p><p style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); text-transform: none; line-height: 1.75em; text-indent: 2em; letter-spacing: normal; font-family: &quot;Segoe UI&quot;, &quot;Lucida Grande&quot;, Helvetica, Arial, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, FreeSans, Arimo, &quot;Droid Sans&quot;, &quot;wenquanyi micro hei&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB W3&quot;, FontAwesome, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; font-style: normal; font-weight: 400; word-spacing: 0px; white-space: normal; box-sizing: border-box; orphans: 2; widows: 2; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; text-decoration-style: initial; text-decoration-color: initial; overflow-wrap: break-word;\"><a title=\"\" href=\"https://www.jihexian.com/article/detail/id/292.html\" target=\"_self\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-family: 微软雅黑, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;; font-size: 14px; box-sizing: border-box;\">几何线微信小程序商城系统</span></a><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-family: 微软雅黑, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;; font-size: 14px; box-sizing: border-box;\">是钦州市友加信息科技有限公司自主研发的一款帮助商家赚钱的商城系统，功能完善、开源免费，支持二次开发，致力解决商家开店、经营、揽客的问题，助力商家畅享小程序引领风潮的巨大红利。<br style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; box-sizing: border-box;\"/></span></p><p style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); text-transform: none; line-height: 1.75em; text-indent: 2em; letter-spacing: normal; font-family: &quot;Segoe UI&quot;, &quot;Lucida Grande&quot;, Helvetica, Arial, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, FreeSans, Arimo, &quot;Droid Sans&quot;, &quot;wenquanyi micro hei&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB W3&quot;, FontAwesome, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; font-style: normal; font-weight: 400; word-spacing: 0px; white-space: normal; box-sizing: border-box; orphans: 2; widows: 2; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; text-decoration-style: initial; text-decoration-color: initial; overflow-wrap: break-word;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-family: 微软雅黑, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;; font-size: 14px; box-sizing: border-box;\">系统适用于零售百货、生鲜果蔬、餐饮、婚庆、服装、艺术品、智慧景区、酒店、家具、汽车等行业。<br/></span></p><p style=\"line-height: 2em;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(51, 51, 51); text-transform: none; text-indent: 28px; letter-spacing: normal; font-family: 微软雅黑, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;; font-size: 14px; font-style: normal; font-weight: 400; word-spacing: 0px; float: none; display: inline !important; white-space: normal; orphans: 2; widows: 2; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; text-decoration-style: initial; text-decoration-color: initial;\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; &nbsp;<span style=\"color: rgb(51, 51, 51); text-transform: none; text-indent: 28px; letter-spacing: normal; font-family: 微软雅黑,Microsoft YaHei; font-size: 14px; font-style: normal; font-weight: 400; word-spacing: 0px; float: none; display: inline !important; white-space: normal; orphans: 2; widows: 2; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; text-decoration-style: initial; text-decoration-color: initial;\">根据对比其他微信商城系统，我们推出基础版小程序本身开源免费，但营销插件、安装服务、服务器和页面设计是收费的项目。我们现在做了一个非常优惠的套餐，3000元包一个无线流量，1m带宽的服务器（880），赠送安装对接服务、二级域名一个、https证书和页面调整服务（定制版根据商家要求另计）。次年如果不用其他服务的，每年只需要支付服务器及证书的费用，大概是1000块左右。</span></span></p><p style=\"line-height: 2em;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(51, 51, 51); text-transform: none; text-indent: 28px; letter-spacing: normal; font-family: 微软雅黑,Microsoft YaHei; font-size: 14px; font-style: normal; font-weight: 400; word-spacing: 0px; float: none; display: inline !important; white-space: normal; orphans: 2; widows: 2; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; text-decoration-style: initial; text-decoration-color: initial;\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; 以下是我们通过对比其他，推出自己公司的产品价格：</span></p><table><tbody><tr><td width=\"352\" valign=\"top\" style=\"-ms-word-break: break-all;\"><strong><span style=\"color: rgb(0, 176, 80); font-family: Segoe UI;\">类项</span></strong><br/></td><td width=\"352\" valign=\"top\" style=\"-ms-word-break: break-all;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(0, 176, 80);\"><strong>基本版</strong></span><br/></td><td width=\"352\" valign=\"top\" style=\"-ms-word-break: break-all;\"><strong><span style=\"color: rgb(0, 176, 80);\">定制版</span></strong><br/></td></tr><tr><td width=\"352\" valign=\"top\" style=\"-ms-word-break: break-all;\"><p>几何线<br/></p></td><td width=\"352\" valign=\"top\" style=\"-ms-word-break: break-all;\">程序免费<br/></td><td width=\"352\" valign=\"top\" style=\"-ms-word-break: break-all;\">4800元起<br/></td></tr><tr><td width=\"352\" valign=\"top\" style=\"-ms-word-break: break-all;\">某赞商城<br/></td><td width=\"352\" valign=\"top\" style=\"-ms-word-break: break-all;\">4800元起<br/></td><td width=\"352\" valign=\"top\" style=\"-ms-word-break: break-all;\">8800元起<br/></td></tr><tr><td width=\"352\" valign=\"top\" style=\"-ms-word-break: break-all;\">其他商城<br/></td><td width=\"352\" valign=\"top\" style=\"-ms-word-break: break-all;\">5000元起<br/></td><td width=\"352\" valign=\"top\" style=\"-ms-word-break: break-all;\">8000元起<br/></td></tr></tbody></table><p>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;<span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑,Microsoft YaHei; font-size: 14px;\">&nbsp;</span></p><p><span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑,Microsoft YaHei; font-size: 14px;\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;欢迎大家联系选购，几何线将竭诚为您服务：</span></p><p style=\"text-align: center;\"><img title=\"微信图片_20180809092649.jpg\" src=\"/Uploads/Editor/2018-09-10/5b95d626030da.jpg\"/></p>',0),(295,'<p style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 8px 0px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); text-transform: none; line-height: 24px; text-indent: 0px; letter-spacing: normal; font-family: 微软雅黑, &quot;Lantinghei SC&quot;, &quot;Open Sans&quot;, Arial, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, STHeiti, &quot;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&quot;, SimSun, sans-serif; font-size: medium; font-style: normal; font-weight: 400; word-spacing: 0px; display: block; white-space: normal; table-layout: fixed; -ms-word-break: break-all; orphans: 2; widows: 2; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; text-decoration-style: initial; text-decoration-color: initial;\"><strong style=\"font-weight: bold;\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; 1、纯小程序创业</strong></p><p style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 8px 0px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); text-transform: none; line-height: 24px; text-indent: 0px; letter-spacing: normal; font-family: 微软雅黑, &quot;Lantinghei SC&quot;, &quot;Open Sans&quot;, Arial, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, STHeiti, &quot;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&quot;, SimSun, sans-serif; font-size: medium; font-style: normal; font-weight: 400; word-spacing: 0px; display: block; white-space: normal; table-layout: fixed; -ms-word-break: break-all; orphans: 2; widows: 2; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; text-decoration-style: initial; text-decoration-color: initial;\">　　纯小程序创业对现有产品的功能进行延伸，开发一个与现有app相辅相成的小程序。通过小程序的高扩散性，解决app传播率低的问题。比如:摩拜、滴滴、打卡助手等。或者，从0到1全新设计研发自己的小程序，1个小程序就1个功能。比如:亲戚关系、群play、手持弹幕、形色识花等。</p><p style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 8px 0px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); text-transform: none; line-height: 24px; text-indent: 0px; letter-spacing: normal; font-family: 微软雅黑, &quot;Lantinghei SC&quot;, &quot;Open Sans&quot;, Arial, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, STHeiti, &quot;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&quot;, SimSun, sans-serif; font-size: medium; font-style: normal; font-weight: 400; word-spacing: 0px; display: block; white-space: normal; table-layout: fixed; -ms-word-break: break-all; orphans: 2; widows: 2; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; text-decoration-style: initial; text-decoration-color: initial;\">　　小程序有大量的访问量后，再根据用户画像进行商业变现。比如&quot;手持弹幕&quot;的使用场景大部分是演唱会，用户群体基本属于粉丝群。小程序制作方可往明星周边等娱乐产业进行转移，最后实现转化变现。</p><p style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 8px 0px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); text-transform: none; line-height: 24px; text-indent: 0px; letter-spacing: normal; font-family: 微软雅黑, &quot;Lantinghei SC&quot;, &quot;Open Sans&quot;, Arial, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, STHeiti, &quot;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&quot;, SimSun, sans-serif; font-size: medium; font-style: normal; font-weight: 400; word-spacing: 0px; display: block; white-space: normal; table-layout: fixed; -ms-word-break: break-all; orphans: 2; widows: 2; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; text-decoration-style: initial; text-decoration-color: initial;\"><strong style=\"font-weight: bold;\">　　2、小程序商店</strong></p><p style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 8px 0px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); text-transform: none; line-height: 24px; text-indent: 0px; letter-spacing: normal; font-family: 微软雅黑, &quot;Lantinghei SC&quot;, &quot;Open Sans&quot;, Arial, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, STHeiti, &quot;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&quot;, SimSun, sans-serif; font-size: medium; font-style: normal; font-weight: 400; word-spacing: 0px; display: block; white-space: normal; table-layout: fixed; -ms-word-break: break-all; orphans: 2; widows: 2; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; text-decoration-style: initial; text-decoration-color: initial;\">　　小程序商店也就是&quot;小程序聚合平台&quot;。前期收录所有小程序，进行免费展示。待知名度、访问量和转化量做起来后，转为收费模式(摊位费、推广费)。</p><p style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 8px 0px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); text-transform: none; line-height: 24px; text-indent: 0px; letter-spacing: normal; font-family: 微软雅黑, &quot;Lantinghei SC&quot;, &quot;Open Sans&quot;, Arial, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, STHeiti, &quot;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&quot;, SimSun, sans-serif; font-size: medium; font-style: normal; font-weight: 400; word-spacing: 0px; display: block; white-space: normal; table-layout: fixed; -ms-word-break: break-all; orphans: 2; widows: 2; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; text-decoration-style: initial; text-decoration-color: initial;\">　　这是目前市面上最普遍的小程序盈利模式。技术型公司利用已有的技术优势，迅速接入小程序技术，为企业、商家提供小程序开发服务，此外，还可衍生出招商加盟业务，为不懂技术的代理商提供技术支持。</p><p style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 8px 0px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); text-transform: none; line-height: 24px; text-indent: 0px; letter-spacing: normal; font-family: 微软雅黑, &quot;Lantinghei SC&quot;, &quot;Open Sans&quot;, Arial, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, STHeiti, &quot;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&quot;, SimSun, sans-serif; font-size: medium; font-style: normal; font-weight: 400; word-spacing: 0px; display: block; white-space: normal; table-layout: fixed; -ms-word-break: break-all; orphans: 2; widows: 2; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; text-decoration-style: initial; text-decoration-color: initial;\">　　作为专业的微信第三方平台开发服务商，比特网络科技拥有海量微信营销成功案例。旗下产品包括微商城、会员、营销等产品矩阵，企业专注于微信小程序商城深度开发运营。为商家提供定制微商城系统，且配合粉丝管理、营销推广、分销等系统，为企业提供成完善的移动电商服务。目前比特网络科技小程序正在火热招商加盟中，欢迎前来咨询。</p><p style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 8px 0px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); text-transform: none; line-height: 24px; text-indent: 0px; letter-spacing: normal; font-family: 微软雅黑, &quot;Lantinghei SC&quot;, &quot;Open Sans&quot;, Arial, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, STHeiti, &quot;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&quot;, SimSun, sans-serif; font-size: medium; font-style: normal; font-weight: 400; word-spacing: 0px; display: block; white-space: normal; table-layout: fixed; -ms-word-break: break-all; orphans: 2; widows: 2; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; text-decoration-style: initial; text-decoration-color: initial;\"><strong style=\"font-weight: bold;\">　　4、内容电商</strong></p><p style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 8px 0px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); text-transform: none; line-height: 24px; text-indent: 0px; letter-spacing: normal; font-family: 微软雅黑, &quot;Lantinghei SC&quot;, &quot;Open Sans&quot;, Arial, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, STHeiti, &quot;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&quot;, SimSun, sans-serif; font-size: medium; font-style: normal; font-weight: 400; word-spacing: 0px; display: block; white-space: normal; table-layout: fixed; -ms-word-break: break-all; orphans: 2; widows: 2; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; text-decoration-style: initial; text-decoration-color: initial;\"><strong style=\"font-weight: bold;\">　&nbsp; </strong>内容电商在公众号等内容平台发布优质内容，并在文章中插入小程序卡片或小程序码。通过内容激发读者的购买冲动，引导其进入小程序购买商品，从而实现&quot;内容→购买&quot;的转化。比如美丽说、虎Cares职场物欲清单等。</p><p style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 8px 0px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); text-transform: none; line-height: 24px; text-indent: 0px; letter-spacing: normal; font-family: 微软雅黑, &quot;Lantinghei SC&quot;, &quot;Open Sans&quot;, Arial, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, STHeiti, &quot;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&quot;, SimSun, sans-serif; font-size: medium; font-style: normal; font-weight: 400; word-spacing: 0px; display: block; white-space: normal; table-layout: fixed; -ms-word-break: break-all; orphans: 2; widows: 2; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; text-decoration-style: initial; text-decoration-color: initial;\"><strong style=\"font-weight: bold;\">　　5、社群电商</strong></p><p style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 8px 0px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); text-transform: none; line-height: 24px; text-indent: 0px; letter-spacing: normal; font-family: 微软雅黑, &quot;Lantinghei SC&quot;, &quot;Open Sans&quot;, Arial, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, STHeiti, &quot;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&quot;, SimSun, sans-serif; font-size: medium; font-style: normal; font-weight: 400; word-spacing: 0px; display: block; white-space: normal; table-layout: fixed; -ms-word-break: break-all; orphans: 2; widows: 2; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; text-decoration-style: initial; text-decoration-color: initial;\">　　社群电商通过一系列社交玩法，让小程序在微信等社群中散发开来，从而引发购买行为。如YOGAN摇杆等。其实，内容和社交电商实质上是将以往的H5商城或第三方购物平台替换成小程序。但因小程序的触达更快更准确，所以内容和社交的引流效果会好非常多。</p><p style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 8px 0px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); text-transform: none; line-height: 24px; text-indent: 0px; letter-spacing: normal; font-family: 微软雅黑, &quot;Lantinghei SC&quot;, &quot;Open Sans&quot;, Arial, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, STHeiti, &quot;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&quot;, SimSun, sans-serif; font-size: medium; font-style: normal; font-weight: 400; word-spacing: 0px; display: block; white-space: normal; table-layout: fixed; -ms-word-break: break-all; orphans: 2; widows: 2; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; text-decoration-style: initial; text-decoration-color: initial;\"><strong style=\"font-weight: bold;\">　　6、O2O服务</strong></p><p style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 8px 0px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); text-transform: none; line-height: 24px; text-indent: 0px; letter-spacing: normal; font-family: 微软雅黑, &quot;Lantinghei SC&quot;, &quot;Open Sans&quot;, Arial, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, STHeiti, &quot;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&quot;, SimSun, sans-serif; font-size: medium; font-style: normal; font-weight: 400; word-spacing: 0px; display: block; white-space: normal; table-layout: fixed; -ms-word-break: break-all; orphans: 2; widows: 2; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; text-decoration-style: initial; text-decoration-color: initial;\">　　O2O服务利用小程序线上的强引流性，将用户引导到线下门店，促成转化。以餐馆为例，消费者从附近的小程序、社交分享、文内广告等途径进到餐馆的小程序，领取抵扣券后前往餐馆消费。消费后，店家还能留存用户信息，建立会员体系，进一步了解用户的消费习惯、偏好等，最后针对性地做喜好推荐、会员优惠等。目前，通过小程序发放优惠券引流的典型例子有:星巴克用星说、麦当劳等。</p><p style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 8px 0px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); text-transform: none; line-height: 24px; text-indent: 0px; letter-spacing: normal; font-family: 微软雅黑, &quot;Lantinghei SC&quot;, &quot;Open Sans&quot;, Arial, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, STHeiti, &quot;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&quot;, SimSun, sans-serif; font-size: medium; font-style: normal; font-weight: 400; word-spacing: 0px; display: block; white-space: normal; table-layout: fixed; -ms-word-break: break-all; orphans: 2; widows: 2; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; text-decoration-style: initial; text-decoration-color: initial;\"><strong style=\"font-weight: bold;\">　　7、小程序周边服务</strong></p><p style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 8px 0px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); text-transform: none; line-height: 24px; text-indent: 0px; letter-spacing: normal; font-family: 微软雅黑, &quot;Lantinghei SC&quot;, &quot;Open Sans&quot;, Arial, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, STHeiti, &quot;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&quot;, SimSun, sans-serif; font-size: medium; font-style: normal; font-weight: 400; word-spacing: 0px; display: block; white-space: normal; table-layout: fixed; -ms-word-break: break-all; orphans: 2; widows: 2; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; text-decoration-style: initial; text-decoration-color: initial;\">　　小程序周边服务包括:小程序行业数据统计分析、小程序资讯媒体、小程序联盟、小程序咨询服务等。</p><p style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 8px 0px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); text-transform: none; line-height: 24px; text-indent: 0px; letter-spacing: normal; font-family: 微软雅黑, &quot;Lantinghei SC&quot;, &quot;Open Sans&quot;, Arial, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, STHeiti, &quot;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&quot;, SimSun, sans-serif; font-size: medium; font-style: normal; font-weight: 400; word-spacing: 0px; display: block; white-space: normal; table-layout: fixed; -ms-word-break: break-all; orphans: 2; widows: 2; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; text-decoration-style: initial; text-decoration-color: initial;\">　　当然了，小程序的盈利模式绝不只有以上几种。但有一点一定要记住:无论您打算以哪种方式进入，一定要快!小程序创业必须直截了当，越早启动越好。</p><p style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 8px 0px; text-align: right; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); text-transform: none; line-height: 24px; text-indent: 0px; letter-spacing: normal; font-family: 微软雅黑, &quot;Lantinghei SC&quot;, &quot;Open Sans&quot;, Arial, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, STHeiti, &quot;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&quot;, SimSun, sans-serif; font-size: medium; font-style: normal; font-weight: 400; word-spacing: 0px; display: block; white-space: normal; table-layout: fixed; -ms-word-break: break-all; orphans: 2; widows: 2; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; text-decoration-style: initial; text-decoration-color: initial;\"><span style=\"text-align: center; color: rgb(64, 64, 64); text-transform: none; text-indent: 0px; letter-spacing: normal; font-family: 微软雅黑, &quot;Lantinghei SC&quot;, &quot;Open Sans&quot;, Arial, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, STHeiti, &quot;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&quot;, SimSun, sans-serif; font-size: 12px; font-style: normal; font-weight: 400; word-spacing: 0px; float: none; display: inline !important; white-space: normal; orphans: 2; widows: 2; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; text-decoration-style: initial; text-decoration-color: initial;\">来源：今日头条　|　李大东　|　2018-09-04</span></p><p><br/></p>',0),(296,'<p style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; text-align: justify; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); text-transform: none; line-height: 1.5em; text-indent: 2em; letter-spacing: normal; font-family: arial; font-size: 16px; font-style: normal; font-weight: 400; word-spacing: 0px; white-space: normal; orphans: 2; widows: 2; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; text-decoration-style: initial; text-decoration-color: initial;\">小程序成为巨头涌入的风口，集齐了BAT的青睐。在这场神仙打架的硝烟中，究竟着怎样的机会和挑战？</p><p style=\"margin: 22px 0px 0px; padding: 0px; text-align: justify; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); text-transform: none; line-height: 1.5em; text-indent: 2em; letter-spacing: normal; font-family: arial; font-size: 16px; font-style: normal; font-weight: 400; word-spacing: 0px; white-space: normal; orphans: 2; widows: 2; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; text-decoration-style: initial; text-decoration-color: initial;\">近日，瑞幸咖啡和腾讯战略合作，咖啡界再次演变为AT之间的战局。为何腾讯频频入局线下场景，剑指阿里？</p><p style=\"margin: 22px 0px 0px; padding: 0px; text-align: justify; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); text-transform: none; line-height: 1.5em; text-indent: 2em; letter-spacing: normal; font-family: arial; font-size: 16px; font-style: normal; font-weight: 400; word-spacing: 0px; white-space: normal; orphans: 2; widows: 2; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; text-decoration-style: initial; text-decoration-color: initial;\">众所周知，对于腾讯发力电商，入局零售这一点似乎在京东接管拍拍那一刻已经划下了句号。但是，在近一年的时间内，腾讯却在紧锣密鼓地布局智慧零售，通过微信独有的生态激发自身在对线下实体的数字化能力。</p><p style=\"margin: 22px 0px 0px; padding: 0px; text-align: justify; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); text-transform: none; line-height: 1.5em; text-indent: 2em; letter-spacing: normal; font-family: arial; font-size: 16px; font-style: normal; font-weight: 400; word-spacing: 0px; white-space: normal; orphans: 2; widows: 2; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; text-decoration-style: initial; text-decoration-color: initial;\">2018年4月，马化腾曾在中国“互联网+”数字峰会上，以“一个目标、三种角色、五个领域、七个工具”形容腾讯的定位，其中七个工具就包括公众号、小程序、微信支付、社交广告、企业微信、ABC（大数据、AI、云计算）还有安全工具。</p><p style=\"margin: 22px 0px 0px; padding: 0px; text-align: justify; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); text-transform: none; line-height: 1.5em; text-indent: 2em; letter-spacing: normal; font-family: arial; font-size: 16px; font-style: normal; font-weight: 400; word-spacing: 0px; white-space: normal; orphans: 2; widows: 2; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; text-decoration-style: initial; text-decoration-color: initial;\">近日，腾讯也正在力推企业微信。“在这七个工具里，企业微信属于承上启下的角色，我们希望将腾讯整个社会化的能力和工具，与大家的需求融合，一起来助力各个企业。”企业微信产品部总经理卢青伟说。毋庸置疑，对于通过社交托底的微信生态以C端的能量见长。企业微信释放出来的信号是腾讯正发动一场B端的战役。</p><p style=\"margin: 22px 0px 0px; padding: 0px; text-align: justify; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); text-transform: none; line-height: 1.5em; text-indent: 2em; letter-spacing: normal; font-family: arial; font-size: 16px; font-style: normal; font-weight: 400; word-spacing: 0px; white-space: normal; orphans: 2; widows: 2; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; text-decoration-style: initial; text-decoration-color: initial;\">更为重要的是，这场B端战役的“秘密武器”在于小程序。</p><p style=\"margin: 22px 0px 0px; padding: 0px; text-align: justify; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); text-transform: none; line-height: 1.5em; text-indent: 2em; letter-spacing: normal; font-family: arial; font-size: 16px; font-style: normal; font-weight: 400; word-spacing: 0px; white-space: normal; orphans: 2; widows: 2; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; text-decoration-style: initial; text-decoration-color: initial;\">AT局</p><p style=\"margin: 22px 0px 0px; padding: 0px; text-align: justify; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); text-transform: none; line-height: 1.5em; text-indent: 2em; letter-spacing: normal; font-family: arial; font-size: 16px; font-style: normal; font-weight: 400; word-spacing: 0px; white-space: normal; orphans: 2; widows: 2; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; text-decoration-style: initial; text-decoration-color: initial;\">在小程序赛道上BAT已经入局。在这场号称取代APP的运动的硝烟中谁会胜出，首先还是用家底说话了。</p><p style=\"margin: 22px 0px 0px; padding: 0px; text-align: justify; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); text-transform: none; line-height: 1.5em; text-indent: 2em; letter-spacing: normal; font-family: arial; font-size: 16px; font-style: normal; font-weight: 400; word-spacing: 0px; white-space: normal; orphans: 2; widows: 2; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; text-decoration-style: initial; text-decoration-color: initial;\">小程序构建的是一个“即插即用”“用完即走”的轻应用，对于BAT小程序的比拼有三大因素：流量、场景、技术。</p><p style=\"margin: 22px 0px 0px; padding: 0px; text-align: justify; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); text-transform: none; line-height: 1.5em; text-indent: 2em; letter-spacing: normal; font-family: arial; font-size: 16px; font-style: normal; font-weight: 400; word-spacing: 0px; white-space: normal; orphans: 2; widows: 2; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; text-decoration-style: initial; text-decoration-color: initial;\">首先，从技术来看，诸如BAT这样的巨无霸而言，底层技术的构建并不会建立多高的壁垒，腾讯云、阿里云的能力难分高下，而致力于未来三十年或者更长时间的人工智能的百度也不是问题，关键之关键还是要看不同商业生态延展出来的能量。</p><p style=\"margin: 22px 0px 0px; padding: 0px; text-align: justify; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); text-transform: none; line-height: 1.5em; text-indent: 2em; letter-spacing: normal; font-family: arial; font-size: 16px; font-style: normal; font-weight: 400; word-spacing: 0px; white-space: normal; orphans: 2; widows: 2; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; text-decoration-style: initial; text-decoration-color: initial;\">从流量上看，根据最新公开数据显示，百度APP日活用户为1.5亿，支付宝全球年度活跃用户为8.7亿（支付宝尚未公布过日活/月活指标）；微信全球月活跃用户则超过10亿，尽管数据单位不同，但在用户基数与活跃度上，在PC时代依托搜索单一模式的百度已经在移联网时代掉队了。</p><p style=\"margin: 22px 0px 0px; padding: 0px; text-align: justify; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); text-transform: none; line-height: 1.5em; text-indent: 2em; letter-spacing: normal; font-family: arial; font-size: 16px; font-style: normal; font-weight: 400; word-spacing: 0px; white-space: normal; orphans: 2; widows: 2; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; text-decoration-style: initial; text-decoration-color: initial;\">另外，还有更为关键的要素——场景。</p><p style=\"margin: 22px 0px 0px; padding: 0px; text-align: justify; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); text-transform: none; line-height: 1.5em; text-indent: 2em; letter-spacing: normal; font-family: arial; font-size: 16px; font-style: normal; font-weight: 400; word-spacing: 0px; white-space: normal; orphans: 2; widows: 2; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; text-decoration-style: initial; text-decoration-color: initial;\">通过交易场景，支付宝能够依托的有生活服务商家、阿里电商平台的商家等，建立其自己的生态闭环，其核心场景的核心优势在于对B端用户连接。与之对比的微信，从高社交粘性中，正逐步构建起“连接一切”的能力，微信之所以能够成为第五大发明，在其具备通吃B、C两端的能力和野心。</p><p style=\"margin: 22px 0px 0px; padding: 0px; text-align: justify; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); text-transform: none; line-height: 1.5em; text-indent: 2em; letter-spacing: normal; font-family: arial; font-size: 16px; font-style: normal; font-weight: 400; word-spacing: 0px; white-space: normal; orphans: 2; widows: 2; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; text-decoration-style: initial; text-decoration-color: initial;\">更为重要的是未来B端的战役在于对场景的占领，从这一点来看，百度几乎已经没戏了。这是一场AT的局。</p><p style=\"margin: 22px 0px 0px; padding: 0px; text-align: justify; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); text-transform: none; line-height: 1.5em; text-indent: 2em; letter-spacing: normal; font-family: arial; font-size: 16px; font-style: normal; font-weight: 400; word-spacing: 0px; white-space: normal; orphans: 2; widows: 2; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; text-decoration-style: initial; text-decoration-color: initial;\">有人说小程序之于微信正如APP之于手机。对于阿里而言，日前，蚂蚁金服井贤栋已经宣布小程序成为未来三年内的战略级项目。</p><p style=\"margin: 22px 0px 0px; padding: 0px; text-align: justify; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); text-transform: none; line-height: 1.5em; text-indent: 2em; letter-spacing: normal; font-family: arial; font-size: 16px; font-style: normal; font-weight: 400; word-spacing: 0px; white-space: normal; orphans: 2; widows: 2; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; text-decoration-style: initial; text-decoration-color: initial;\">除了钉钉和企业微信的对抗。在小程序入口的设置上，微信也经过了一段试错期。由于初期入口过深，用户难以触达，微信小程序在发布的前半年曾在活跃度上遭遇瓶颈，此后微信不断延伸入口，新增公众号跳转、下拉页面、搜一搜等超过60个入口。同理，支付宝也在App内为小程序铺设了35个入口，以更快激活小程序生态。</p><p style=\"margin: 22px 0px 0px; padding: 0px; text-align: justify; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); text-transform: none; line-height: 1.5em; text-indent: 2em; letter-spacing: normal; font-family: arial; font-size: 16px; font-style: normal; font-weight: 400; word-spacing: 0px; white-space: normal; orphans: 2; widows: 2; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; text-decoration-style: initial; text-decoration-color: initial;\">不难想象，又是一场暗战。</p><p style=\"margin: 22px 0px 0px; padding: 0px; text-align: justify; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); text-transform: none; line-height: 1.5em; text-indent: 2em; letter-spacing: normal; font-family: arial; font-size: 16px; font-style: normal; font-weight: 400; word-spacing: 0px; white-space: normal; orphans: 2; widows: 2; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; text-decoration-style: initial; text-decoration-color: initial;\">小程序是赋能场景的利器，无论是线上还是线下。</p><p style=\"margin: 22px 0px 0px; padding: 0px; text-align: justify; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); text-transform: none; line-height: 1.5em; text-indent: 2em; letter-spacing: normal; font-family: arial; font-size: 16px; font-style: normal; font-weight: 400; word-spacing: 0px; white-space: normal; orphans: 2; widows: 2; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; text-decoration-style: initial; text-decoration-color: initial;\">目前，我们似乎已经习惯了拼多多、同程艺龙等小程序营造的“拼团”“砍价”“秒杀”等激发即时性，群体性购物的场景，一种去中心化的购物方式，用拼多多黄峥的话说是“货去找人”的去中心化购物场景。</p><p style=\"margin: 22px 0px 0px; padding: 0px; text-align: justify; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); text-transform: none; line-height: 1.5em; text-indent: 2em; letter-spacing: normal; font-family: arial; font-size: 16px; font-style: normal; font-weight: 400; word-spacing: 0px; white-space: normal; orphans: 2; widows: 2; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; text-decoration-style: initial; text-decoration-color: initial;\">同样，在线下便随着“扫码支付”的普及，“公交+小程序”“加油+小程序”“政务+小乘”“快递+小程序”等等把特定下的场景如在家，在学校，在办公室，在公交车上、在医院等地点，人还事情勾连起来，如春风化雨般连接起用户、商家。</p><p style=\"margin: 22px 0px 0px; padding: 0px; text-align: justify; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); text-transform: none; line-height: 1.5em; text-indent: 2em; letter-spacing: normal; font-family: arial; font-size: 16px; font-style: normal; font-weight: 400; word-spacing: 0px; white-space: normal; orphans: 2; widows: 2; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; text-decoration-style: initial; text-decoration-color: initial;\">小程序进入了B端赋能时代。</p><p style=\"margin: 22px 0px 0px; padding: 0px; text-align: justify; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); text-transform: none; line-height: 1.5em; text-indent: 2em; letter-spacing: normal; font-family: arial; font-size: 16px; font-style: normal; font-weight: 400; word-spacing: 0px; white-space: normal; orphans: 2; widows: 2; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; text-decoration-style: initial; text-decoration-color: initial;\">B端战役</p><p style=\"margin: 22px 0px 0px; padding: 0px; text-align: justify; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); text-transform: none; line-height: 1.5em; text-indent: 2em; letter-spacing: normal; font-family: arial; font-size: 16px; font-style: normal; font-weight: 400; word-spacing: 0px; white-space: normal; orphans: 2; widows: 2; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; text-decoration-style: initial; text-decoration-color: initial;\">据相关数据显示，目前有8600万的线下商户等待着赋能B端的小程序去开发与挖掘，这其中便着无限的商机。</p><p style=\"margin: 22px 0px 0px; padding: 0px; text-align: justify; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); text-transform: none; line-height: 1.5em; text-indent: 2em; letter-spacing: normal; font-family: arial; font-size: 16px; font-style: normal; font-weight: 400; word-spacing: 0px; white-space: normal; orphans: 2; widows: 2; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; text-decoration-style: initial; text-decoration-color: initial;\">根据阿拉丁小程序统计平台和指数平台数据显示，麦当劳8月8日会员节，i麦当劳小程序当日用户访问量是前一日的2.58倍，是后一日的2.62倍；其当日新用户访问量是前一日的2.04倍，是后一日的2.95倍，冲入阿拉丁指数总榜TOP30。</p><p style=\"margin: 22px 0px 0px; padding: 0px; text-align: justify; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); text-transform: none; line-height: 1.5em; text-indent: 2em; letter-spacing: normal; font-family: arial; font-size: 16px; font-style: normal; font-weight: 400; word-spacing: 0px; white-space: normal; orphans: 2; widows: 2; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; text-decoration-style: initial; text-decoration-color: initial;\">今年七夕节美团小程序推出红包裂变活动，通过阿拉丁小程序统计平的台监测数据，可以看到活动当天，其小程序日UV相比日常均值上升了5倍，访问用户中来自分享的占比近六成，活动带来的新用户占比也超过50%。</p><p style=\"margin: 22px 0px 0px; padding: 0px; text-align: justify; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); text-transform: none; line-height: 1.5em; text-indent: 2em; letter-spacing: normal; font-family: arial; font-size: 16px; font-style: normal; font-weight: 400; word-spacing: 0px; white-space: normal; orphans: 2; widows: 2; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; text-decoration-style: initial; text-decoration-color: initial;\">小程序在B端的能力得到真正的展现。</p><p style=\"margin: 22px 0px 0px; padding: 0px; text-align: justify; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); text-transform: none; line-height: 1.5em; text-indent: 2em; letter-spacing: normal; font-family: arial; font-size: 16px; font-style: normal; font-weight: 400; word-spacing: 0px; white-space: normal; orphans: 2; widows: 2; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; text-decoration-style: initial; text-decoration-color: initial;\">为什么腾讯近一年内在线下零售频频发力？用马化腾的话说，除了利用数字技术助力线下传统零售，能够抓住数字化的机遇，能够把人、货、场景几方面全部打通，要不将会失去竞争力。</p><p style=\"margin: 22px 0px 0px; padding: 0px; text-align: justify; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); text-transform: none; line-height: 1.5em; text-indent: 2em; letter-spacing: normal; font-family: arial; font-size: 16px; font-style: normal; font-weight: 400; word-spacing: 0px; white-space: normal; orphans: 2; widows: 2; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; text-decoration-style: initial; text-decoration-color: initial;\">腾讯发现线上和线下零售的融合开始了，这个融合的主战场在线下，这种大融合可能会对以后的社会生活产生深远的影响，腾讯必须参与进来。</p><p style=\"margin: 22px 0px 0px; padding: 0px; text-align: justify; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); text-transform: none; line-height: 1.5em; text-indent: 2em; letter-spacing: normal; font-family: arial; font-size: 16px; font-style: normal; font-weight: 400; word-spacing: 0px; white-space: normal; orphans: 2; widows: 2; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; text-decoration-style: initial; text-decoration-color: initial;\">腾讯方面出手可谓快、准、狠，从今年1月起，短短3个月，投资了家乐福、万达商业和海澜之家(600398,股吧)，投资额已达200亿。再加上去年投资的每日优鲜、美团点评、永辉超市(601933,股吧)、超级物种、唯品会，估计腾讯在新零售领域已砸了超过500亿。</p><p style=\"margin: 22px 0px 0px; padding: 0px; text-align: justify; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); text-transform: none; line-height: 1.5em; text-indent: 2em; letter-spacing: normal; font-family: arial; font-size: 16px; font-style: normal; font-weight: 400; word-spacing: 0px; white-space: normal; orphans: 2; widows: 2; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; text-decoration-style: initial; text-decoration-color: initial;\">一系列动作，无外乎是进行B端场景的争夺。</p><p style=\"margin: 22px 0px 0px; padding: 0px; text-align: justify; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); text-transform: none; line-height: 1.5em; text-indent: 2em; letter-spacing: normal; font-family: arial; font-size: 16px; font-style: normal; font-weight: 400; word-spacing: 0px; white-space: normal; orphans: 2; widows: 2; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; text-decoration-style: initial; text-decoration-color: initial;\">作为电商基因的阿里自不必说，自从打响新零售战役以来，一直在打通线上线下会员、支付、货品。在面向实体零售不仅通过资本去推推进合作，同时还孵化了盒马鲜生希望在这个链路上跑通。</p><p style=\"margin: 22px 0px 0px; padding: 0px; text-align: justify; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); text-transform: none; line-height: 1.5em; text-indent: 2em; letter-spacing: normal; font-family: arial; font-size: 16px; font-style: normal; font-weight: 400; word-spacing: 0px; white-space: normal; orphans: 2; widows: 2; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; text-decoration-style: initial; text-decoration-color: initial;\">支付宝小程序战略具有四个特点：</p><p style=\"margin: 22px 0px 0px; padding: 0px; text-align: justify; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); text-transform: none; line-height: 1.5em; text-indent: 2em; letter-spacing: normal; font-family: arial; font-size: 16px; font-style: normal; font-weight: 400; word-spacing: 0px; white-space: normal; orphans: 2; widows: 2; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; text-decoration-style: initial; text-decoration-color: initial;\">一是，高度聚焦本地商务和服务，围绕钱的流转，打各种交易场景，所以诸如内容、游戏、社交这些线上流量的品类，一开始不在考虑中。</p><p style=\"margin: 22px 0px 0px; padding: 0px; text-align: justify; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); text-transform: none; line-height: 1.5em; text-indent: 2em; letter-spacing: normal; font-family: arial; font-size: 16px; font-style: normal; font-weight: 400; word-spacing: 0px; white-space: normal; orphans: 2; widows: 2; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; text-decoration-style: initial; text-decoration-color: initial;\">二是高度重视商家赋能，主打服务交易升级。第一个爆点集中在“信用分”上，信用免押成为第一个爆品，帮助商家降低押金门槛，迅速捕获优质信用客户，提升转化率。再比如会员系统、调度系统、人脸识别、融资担保。</p><p style=\"margin: 22px 0px 0px; padding: 0px; text-align: justify; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); text-transform: none; line-height: 1.5em; text-indent: 2em; letter-spacing: normal; font-family: arial; font-size: 16px; font-style: normal; font-weight: 400; word-spacing: 0px; white-space: normal; orphans: 2; widows: 2; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; text-decoration-style: initial; text-decoration-color: initial;\">三是高门槛，更类似ios操作系统，更封闭但也更强调严肃安全品质，所以微信门店这种告示牌类小程序你是看不到的。</p><p style=\"margin: 22px 0px 0px; padding: 0px; text-align: justify; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); text-transform: none; line-height: 1.5em; text-indent: 2em; letter-spacing: normal; font-family: arial; font-size: 16px; font-style: normal; font-weight: 400; word-spacing: 0px; white-space: normal; orphans: 2; widows: 2; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; text-decoration-style: initial; text-decoration-color: initial;\">四最关键，全流量分发。很多人说支付宝没有流量红利，但这回支付宝是全平台分发，手淘、天猫、高德地图……等等阿里系app上都可以复用和触发。如果真的做到这个流量红利也不得了。</p><p style=\"margin: 22px 0px 0px; padding: 0px; text-align: justify; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); text-transform: none; line-height: 1.5em; text-indent: 2em; letter-spacing: normal; font-family: arial; font-size: 16px; font-style: normal; font-weight: 400; word-spacing: 0px; white-space: normal; orphans: 2; widows: 2; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; text-decoration-style: initial; text-decoration-color: initial;\">然而，伴随着微信互联网时代的到来，微信小程序日活跃账户超2亿，是目前微信生态环境不可忽视的一环，小程序生态已然发力，正呈现不断上升的趋势，迈入高速发展的快车道，覆盖政务民生，交通出行、金融、旅游、酒店、餐饮、零售等多个行业。</p><p style=\"margin: 22px 0px 0px; padding: 0px; text-align: justify; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); text-transform: none; line-height: 1.5em; text-indent: 2em; letter-spacing: normal; font-family: arial; font-size: 16px; font-style: normal; font-weight: 400; word-spacing: 0px; white-space: normal; orphans: 2; widows: 2; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; text-decoration-style: initial; text-decoration-color: initial;\">小程序已经引爆B端战役。</p><p style=\"text-align: right;\">------转载自《<span style=\"color: rgb(102, 102, 102); text-transform: none; text-indent: 0px; letter-spacing: normal; font-family: 微软雅黑, 宋体; font-size: 14px; font-style: normal; font-weight: 400; word-spacing: 0px; float: none; display: inline !important;  orphans: 2; widows: 2; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; text-decoration-style: initial; text-decoration-color: initial;\">&nbsp;</span>和讯名家》</p>',0),(297,'<p>小程序商城后台操作流程</p>',0),(298,'<p style=\"text-align: left; line-height: 2em; text-indent: 2em;\"><span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑,Microsoft YaHei;\">1.打开微信公众平台 <a href=\"https://mp.weixin.qq.com/\">https://mp.weixin.qq.com/</a>，在右上角点击「立即注册」</span></p><p style=\"text-align: center; line-height: 2em;\"><span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑,Microsoft YaHei;\"><img title=\"1.png\" src=\"/Uploads/Editor/2018-09-11/5b9783687dd91.png\"/></span></p><p style=\"line-height: 2em; text-indent: 2em;\"><span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑,Microsoft YaHei;\">2.选择第三个，「小程序」的选项。</span></p><p style=\"text-align: center; line-height: 2em;\"><span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑,Microsoft YaHei;\"><img title=\"2.png\" src=\"/Uploads/Editor/2018-09-11/5b9783a800da8.png\"/></span></p><p style=\"line-height: 2em; text-indent: 2em;\"><span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑,Microsoft YaHei;\">3.填写用户的基本信息，每个邮箱仅能申请一个小程序，填写完成以后会发送一封确认邮件到邮箱。</span></p><p style=\"text-align: center; line-height: 2em;\"><span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑,Microsoft YaHei;\"><img title=\"3.png\" src=\"/Uploads/Editor/2018-09-11/5b9783d10e1be.png\"/></span></p><p style=\"line-height: 2em; text-indent: 2em;\"><span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑,Microsoft YaHei;\">4.从邮箱打开确认链接，完善注册信息，目前仅限企业、政府、媒体、其他组织注册，个人暂时不能注册，这里要提醒的是注册完成以后就只能通过300认证的来通过为认证了，所以务必在这一步进行企业认证。</span></p><p style=\"text-align: center; line-height: 2em;\"><span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑,Microsoft YaHei;\"><img title=\"4.png\" src=\"/Uploads/Editor/2018-09-11/5b9784196b523.png\"/></span></p><p style=\"line-height: 2em; text-indent: 2em;\"><span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑,Microsoft YaHei;\">5.填写完信息即可注册成功，成功后即可跳转到登录成功首页，登录成功后还需要认证企业信息方可使用。</span></p><p style=\"text-align: center; line-height: 2em;\"><span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑,Microsoft YaHei;\"><img title=\"5.png\" src=\"/Uploads/Editor/2018-09-11/5b97842ea0973.png\"/></span></p><p style=\"line-height: 2em; text-indent: 2em;\"><span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑,Microsoft YaHei;\">6.小程序信息完善：填写小程序基本信息，包括名称、头像、介绍及服务范围等。</span></p><p style=\"text-align: center; line-height: 2em;\"><span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑,Microsoft YaHei;\"><img title=\"6.png\" src=\"/Uploads/Editor/2018-09-11/5b97844bd98a8.png\"/></span></p><p style=\"line-height: 2em; text-indent: 2em;\"><span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑,Microsoft YaHei;\">7.开发小程序：完成小程序开发者绑定、开发信息配置后，开发者可下载开发者工具、参考开发文档进行小程序的开发和调试。</span></p><p style=\"text-align: center; line-height: 2em;\"><span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑,Microsoft YaHei;\"><img title=\"7.png\" src=\"/Uploads/Editor/2018-09-11/5b978478bd72c.png\"/></span></p><p style=\"text-align: center; line-height: 2em; text-indent: 2em;\"><span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑,Microsoft YaHei;\">8.提交审核和发布：完成小程序开发后，提交代码至微信团队审核，审核通过后即可发布（公测期间暂不支持发布）。<br/></span><img title=\"8.png\" src=\"/Uploads/Editor/2018-09-11/5b9784a59d591.png\"/></p>',0),(299,'<p style=\"text-align:center\"><span style=\"font-size:32px;font-family:&#39;思源黑体 CN Heavy&#39;,&#39;sans-serif&#39;\">几何线小程序系统使用手册</span></p><p style=\"text-align:center\">&nbsp;</p><p style=\"text-align:center\">&nbsp;</p><ol class=\"custom_cn list-paddingleft-1\"><li class=\"list-cn-1-1 list-cn-paddingleft-1\"><p style=\"text-align:left;text-indent:0;lin