></p><p style=\"margin: 5px 0px; text-align: left; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); text-transform: none; line-height: 1.75em; text-indent: 2em; letter-spacing: normal; font-family: sans-serif; font-size: 16px; font-style: normal; font-weight: 400; word-spacing: 0px; white-space: normal; orphans: 2; widows: 2; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; text-decoration-style: initial; text-decoration-color: initial;\"><span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑,; font-size: 14px;\">2.发布文章，在上文第二项“系统菜单”中已有说明。</span></p><p style=\"margin: 5px 0px; text-align: left; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); text-transform: none; line-height: 1.75em; text-indent: 2em; letter-spacing: normal; font-family: sans-serif; font-size: 16px; font-style: normal; font-weight: 400; word-spacing: 0px; white-space: normal; orphans: 2; widows: 2; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; text-decoration-style: initial; text-decoration-color: initial;\"><span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑,; font-size: 14px;\">3.发布的文章被删除后，储存在“回收站”，可“还原”也可以永久“清除”。</span></p><p style=\"margin: 5px 0px; text-align: left; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); text-transform: none; line-height: 1.75em; text-indent: 2em; letter-spacing: normal; font-family: sans-serif; font-size: 16px; font-style: normal; font-weight: 400; word-spacing: 0px; white-space: normal; orphans: 2; widows: 2; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; text-decoration-style: initial; text-decoration-color: initial;\"><span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑,; font-size: 14px;\">4.分类管理，是对发布的文章进行分类。</span></p><p style=\"margin: 5px 0px; text-align: left; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); text-transform: none; line-height: 1.75em; text-indent: 2em; letter-spacing: normal; font-family: sans-serif; font-size: 16px; font-style: normal; font-weight: 400; word-spacing: 0px; white-space: normal; orphans: 2; widows: 2; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; text-decoration-style: initial; text-decoration-color: initial;\"><span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑,; font-size: 14px;\">5.评论管理，可对评论进行审核、更新、删除，一般不建议删除，但可以管理审核一些很恶劣的评价。</span></p><p style=\"margin: 5px 0px; text-align: left; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); text-transform: none; line-height: 1.75em; text-indent: 2em; letter-spacing: normal; font-family: sans-serif; font-size: 16px; font-style: normal; font-weight: 400; word-spacing: 0px; white-space: normal; orphans: 2; widows: 2; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; text-decoration-style: initial; text-decoration-color: initial;\"><span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑,; font-size: 14px;\">6.单页管理，对某些页面可以进行重点说明。</span></p><p style=\"margin: 5px 0px; text-align: left; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); text-transform: none; line-height: 1.75em; text-indent: 2em; letter-spacing: normal; font-family: sans-serif; font-size: 16px; font-style: normal; font-weight: 400; word-spacing: 0px; white-space: normal; orphans: 2; widows: 2; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; text-decoration-style: initial; text-decoration-color: initial;\"><span style=\"font-size: 14px;\"><strong><span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑,; font-size: 14px;\" microsoft=\"\"><br/></span></strong></span></p><p style=\"margin: 5px 0px; text-align: left; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); text-transform: none; line-height: 1.75em; text-indent: 2em; letter-spacing: normal; font-family: sans-serif; font-size: 16px; font-style: normal; font-weight: 400; word-spacing: 0px; white-space: normal; orphans: 2; widows: 2; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; text-decoration-style: initial; text-decoration-color: initial;\"><span style=\"font-size: 14px;\"><strong><span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑,; font-size: 14px;\" microsoft=\"\">四、网站</span></strong></span></p><p style=\"margin: 5px 0px; text-align: left; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); text-transform: 